Changes planned for 0.0.2
=========================

CVL:
- Use CAIRO interface instead of cvl_draw_* functions.
- Remove cvl_draw.h/cvl_draw.c

cvtool:
- Add draw command
  line, polygon, circle, ellipse, text
- Add fieldconv command
  to convert to/from different kinds of fields, for example
  double <-> gray; double,double,double <-> RGB, 
  vectors -> needlemaps; int <-> gray; ...
- Remove vectors command
- Rewrite grid command (or remove it)
- Replace foreach command with a similar command that does the same but also
  allows to select frame ranges, similar to the select command



Other plans
===========

CVL:
- Add Sharpening (Unsharp masking, Laplace, ...)
- Add Segmentation framework
- Add Thinning
- Add Distance maps
- Add morphological operators
- Add corner detection
- Add Marr/Hildreth edge detection
- Add Hough transforms
- Add Pyramid framework

cvtool:
- Add sharpen command
  Unsharp masking, Laplace, ...

Documentation:
- Complete the texinfo manual for CVL
